Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田這個名字去不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給我買條煙  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫庫魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:09.09,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給我買條煙  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給我買條煙  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.02,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家叫庫魯斯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留那小鬼到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了與世長辭的姐姐外  他好像無依無靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救救我吧  夏娃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說啊  你竟然是這部動畫的主角  這多麼令人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是說  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給跑腿去買大蠻牛強經果凍飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣…  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這個教堂當上了跑腿兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也心懷感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐對飲料的追求很古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而至於神父大人  真搞不懂他平時在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有山田這個名字  難道真的沒法拯救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田這是啥  我要的分明是大蠻牛強經果凍飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是小蠻牛強經果凍飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹徹底底不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起  只有它有貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就給我跑腿到找出來為止啊

Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  這不是有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折騰了整整一上午啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  有個不好對付的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖約
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個閒工夫理它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在這裡避開它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不妙了  希望它趁早走開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則回不了家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家？去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀掉聖約的神父之處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是另有同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他浮在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是…「香菇」派來的魔爪NEEDLESS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫西美翁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常正確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是西美翁四天王之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說是西美翁四天王？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田  你慌什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西美翁四天王只靠四個人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠四個人  瞬間就擺平了我的同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  徹底完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要問問這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能讓你消逝於此了  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的炮擊是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱不禁風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩你一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了你的神父  他在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還能站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口在癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分變身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓周圍的細胞變化  以此癒合傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  你也是NEEDLESS啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒卡夫卡的莫非不是那神父  而是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐  我們跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對西美翁四天王沒有勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少說廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奮起而戰就只有送死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是BS的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒夠著？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這屏障是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這攻擊對卡夫卡管用卻對我不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百慕大隔空術
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.20,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bermuda  athport

Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  又沒看清怎麼出招的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜反抗西美翁者  一死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是BS的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了  在上頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才明明沒有這麼龐大的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需不需要變幾隻鴿子來欣賞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 接下來把你截成兩段如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是變戲法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人僅限一個NEEDLESS的能力才是大原則  但是他卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由浮空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展超高速攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能無中生有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這宛如…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神  一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  過度人  有沒有聽說過
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.77,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(292,355)}Missing-link

Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過度人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憶往昔  神按照自己的模樣造就了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而人類正在進化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEEDLESS是人類向神的過渡階段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為數眾多的NEEDLESS當中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走在進化最前沿的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱作過度人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就像我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把話說開  我是最為接近神的NEEDLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我牽連了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己自不量力的作對行為了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再問你一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務就是結束他生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算神父大人再怎麼強  也不會是這傢伙的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把你變成屍體再找線索也不遲



Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠變身而讓身體礦質化而進行防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種大招你能持續用多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身的能力消耗很大卡路里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癒合累累的傷痕應該耗了你不少能量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣  時限快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  變身要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用不了NEEDLESS的能力  就與人類無異
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐你現在和你旁邊的小鬼沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名副其實的NEEDLESS  徹底廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕

Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:48.41,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明創生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大西洋上有著船舶或是飛機事故頻發的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被命名為百慕大三角的魔一般的海域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡殘存著創造物體或使物體消失的神的創生之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是擁有創生之力的NEEDLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才吹散了地板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取而代之的是我創造出來的針
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最接近神的NEEDLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些捨不得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是讓遊戲進入尾聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個選項你們擇一便可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原地被活活打死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是掉到下面被刺死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐已經不能再使用能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去真的沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要   到底該怎麼辦好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你去戰鬥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我…戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我對你的力道不抱有任何期望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要動動腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人不過是個魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEEDLESS的能力每人僅限一種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無一例外的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人是NEEDLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使看上去是萬能的  能力卻也只有一種

Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以姐姐為代價存活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不想要那種滋味了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個魔術的機關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看穿它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thinking time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經連癒合傷口的力量都不剩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮空的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏障的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超高速攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無中生有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有種能力能滿足上述的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,time up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂山田  有沒有可以當盾的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  能當作盾的  盾…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濺了人家一身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  淨出洋相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人類要想戰勝我這個過度人級別的NEEDLESS  就好比是做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用魔法那就另當別論
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小屁孩兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是最為接近神的NEEDLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓根就沒有存活的可能性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰看了都知道是飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃姐  我了謎底明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？什麼莫名其妙的語序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您快看這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小屁孩兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就簡稱田中咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的戲法  看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾對魔術師崇拜的五體投地  僅限於不知道謎底之前

Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而觀眾知曉了謎底之後只有一種反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田  說給他聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢說看穿了我的戲法？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就證明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上了  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  小心紮成馬蜂窩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有令地板消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它透明了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力是  讓物體透明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑空弄出來帽子啦刀啦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是讓透明好的東西又重新現形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  你也不是浮在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是站在透明的地板上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以只進行遠距離攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以讓地板透明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了絆住我們的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了不暴露你的腳下有地板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不賴啊  你以什麼為契機發現了這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田拿出來的飲料是轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的身後  飛濺到你的死角的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了透明化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.00,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}透明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只因為看不見你的攻擊才誤以為那是超高速的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了我的能力你們也是死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你再也使用不了能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可未必哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  你明明不該有使用能力的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過了吧  飲料是轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這一罐飲料能起什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.89,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}5000k卡路里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5000k卡路里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以愛喝這飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我愛好怪癖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是為了維持大量消耗卡路里的變身能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才飲料撒了人家一身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量補給  相當充分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧田中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用  我有鐵壁屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐也  第一次有效的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明化的能力…解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而鐵壁屏障  其實就是一堵水泥牆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了材質就能輕輕鬆鬆毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻遜的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三流魔術師~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最接近神的NEEDLESS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那節哀順變咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家我就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判決
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖約走遠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為要死翹翹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  那個鐵球  針山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是利用了這棟建築內本來就存在的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  如果不是的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多東西  靠他一個小鬼是搬不動的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定在附近  還有個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊回家去吧  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞煩你們給我帶個路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到神父那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個悲劇一般的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基多下話領便當
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短短三話就死翹翹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會化基多而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待次回  基多之死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟標題寫的不一樣啊